---
---
<section class="py-32 px-6 relative z-10 bg-zinc-50/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-t border-zinc-100" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-20 group">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight mb-6 text-zinc-950 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105">
        From Requirements to Running Software
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:text-zinc-600">
        We run a structured, low-friction engagement — no months of back-and-forth before a line of code is written.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative">
      <!-- Desktop connecting line -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-16 right-16 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-zinc-200 to-transparent z-0"></div>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl border bg-white border-zinc-200/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 z-10">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-zinc-50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-950 group-hover:bg-zinc-950 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-500 transform group-hover:scale-110 shadow-sm">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:map-point-search-linear" class="text-2xl" style="stroke-width: 1.5;"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-zinc-400 uppercase mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-zinc-900">Step 1</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight mb-3 text-zinc-950">Discover</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-zinc-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          We map your existing workflows, identify friction points, and define the functional requirements with the people who will actually use the system.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl border bg-white border-zinc-200/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 z-10">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-zinc-50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-950 group-hover:bg-zinc-950 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-500 transform group-hover:scale-110 shadow-sm">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:pen-new-square-linear" class="text-2xl" style="stroke-width: 1.5;"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-zinc-400 uppercase mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-zinc-900">Step 2</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight mb-3 text-zinc-950">Design & Build</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-zinc-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          We design the application architecture and build iteratively, keeping your stakeholders in the loop at every milestone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl border bg-white border-zinc-200/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 z-10">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-zinc-50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-950 group-hover:bg-zinc-950 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-500 transform group-hover:scale-110 shadow-sm">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:rocket-linear" class="text-2xl" style="stroke-width: 1.5;"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-zinc-400 uppercase mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-zinc-900">Step 3</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight mb-3 text-zinc-950">Deploy & Support</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-zinc-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          We deploy to your environment and provide ongoing support. The system is yours — fully documented, maintainable, and built to scale.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
